Interface HazelcastProperty

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GroupProperty
    Deprecated.

    @PrivateApi
 @Deprecated
public interface HazelcastProperty
    Interface for Hazelcast Member and Client properties. Deprecated since Hazelcast 3.7. This is private API, don't use it.
